# Best Price Finder - Case study

We need to search in multiple websites, and get the results from multiple sites and display it
Also, display the time taken overall

Query all the sites simultaneously
Whenever any site's result is ready, then display it
finally display total time taken


Example:

Getting a quote from site1
Getting a quote from site2
Getting a quote from site3
Quote{site='site3', price=102}
Quote{site='site2', price=106}
Quote{site='site1', price=100}
Retrieved all quotes in 2757 msec